          <td><sup>1.</sup> Rounded to the nearest &#x00A3;100,000. Grant as calculated under the Local Government Finance Report (England) and Local Government Finance Report (Wales). This includes the Metropolitan Police special payment, and the effects of floors and ceilings.</td>
